st/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/counter/api/OrderService.java**\n    - Removed Vertx Message and Mutiny dependencies\n    - Changed to String parameter\n\n18. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/counter/OrderServiceImpl.java**\n    - Replaced @ApplicationScoped with @Service\n    - Replaced Vertx EventBus with Spring ApplicationEventPublisher\n    - Added @EventListener for handling OrderUp events\n    - Changed persist() to save()\n    - Removed Mutiny reactive patterns\n\n#### Web Module:\n19. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/web/CoffeeshopApiResource.java**\n    - Replaced JAX-RS annotations with Spring MVC (@RestController, @PostMapping)\n    - Replaced @Inject with constructor injection\n    - Changed Response to ResponseEntity\n\n20. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/web/DashboardEndpoint.java**\n    - Replaced JAX-RS annotations with Spring MVC\n    - Replaced Vertx EventBus with Spring ApplicationEventPublisher\n    - Changed Multi<String> reactive stream to SseEmitter (Spring SSE)\n\n21. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/web/WebResource.java**\n    - Replaced Qute Template with Thymeleaf Model\n    - Replaced @ConfigProperty with @Value\n    - Changed from @Path to @Controller with @GetMapping\n\n### Key Migration Changes Applied:\n\n1. **Entity Framework**: PanacheEntity/PanacheEntityBase → Standard JPA entities with @Id @GeneratedValue\n2. **Repository Pattern**: PanacheRepository → Spring Data JpaRepository\n3. **Dependency Injection**: @Inject/@ApplicationScoped → Constructor injection with @Service/@Repository\n4. **Event Handling**: Vertx EventBus → Spring ApplicationEventPublisher with @EventListener\n5. **REST API**: JAX-RS (@Path, @POST) → Spring MVC (@RestController, @PostMapping)\n6. **Template Engine**: Qute → Thymeleaf\n7. **Configuration**: @ConfigProperty → @Value\n8. **Reactive Streams**: Mutiny Multi → Spring SseEmitter\n9. **Messaging**: SmallRye Kafka → Spring Events (simplified)\n10. **Database Operations**: persist()/persistAndFlush() → save()\n\nAll files have been successfully written and are ready for the Spring Boot application!"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"df095e3b-f7e3-4e4b-a52d-37a5c6ff1041","uuid":"e7b9228b-8ac2-4959-a7f4-c268e802b22c"}
